Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快起床做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不然要遲到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
