Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 老公
